{"tid":426808,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經?]個人認為《麥兜故事》最攞命既一段","createTime":"2017-10-07T03:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T16:21:49.000Z","uid":81413,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"58d2e2a1367949d0d25df63ff1d4ee2405fb053e","tid":426808,"uid":81413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"後來我先知道，<br />\n一隻火雞由出世到俾人劏，<br />\n都不過係幾個月之間既事。<br />\n啫係話，隻火雞死咗之後，同我地一齊既日子，仲長過佢自己本身條命。<br />\n<br />\n我仲發覺到，<br />\n火雞既味道，未食同食第一啖之間，已經係最高峰。<br />\n之後，不過都係食開就食埋落去咁解。<br />\n<br />\n我無哲學家既頭腦，唔知呢兩樣野要得出啲咩道理。<br />\n但係呢啲諗法，係我長大之後，係一啲同聖誕節無關既日子，無端端咁係我腦部出現過兩三次。<br />\n<br />\n一次，係我自己既婚宴上。<br />\n<br />\n一次，係我媽媽火化嗰日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlmBMIOxvsI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDlmBMIOxvsI&d=SUUlpUkacCygxzKbGvHTM%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=676737bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlmBMIOxvsI</a><br />\n<br />\n屌，麥兜何止小朋友唔啱睇，大人都唔好亂咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf70877c561c3704e9ed1e2ebbaf9569fecd4c4","tid":426808,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61b2c57cdcf1e7e03fd7c561f29b0f2d05b8e53","tid":426808,"uid":39739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"菠蘿油王子成套都好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d073cc569e9c4ab3918f8203db48649260c27ffc","tid":426808,"uid":39853,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菠蘿油王子成套都好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揾劉德華配音其實幾襯，有種滄桑感"},{"pid":"3b937800c5b6135a976df5fbec